<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" ng-app="myApp">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= title %></title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat+Alternates:400,700|Open+Sans:400,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <base href="/">
</head>
<body ng-controller="AppCtrl">
  <div class="main-container">

     <style>
      .container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        height: 97%;
      }

      .context {
        width: 60%;
      }

      .container p {
        font-size: 1.5em;
      }

      footer {
        color: #000000;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #FFF;
        padding: 8px;
        height: 3%;
      }
    </style>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="context">
        <p>
          Dear participants:
        </p>
        <p>
          Thank you for taking part in the experiment. I am a graduate student from Institute of Service Science, National Tsing Hua
          University, Taiwan, and I am currently conducting a cognitive study. You will later be asked to participate in three different
          and independent studies; two are autobiographical memory tasks, and one is a brainstorming task. All of the three studies
          will be presented and done on a website. After that, you will be transferred to answer a short questionnaire as the last part.
          The whole experiment might take approximately 20 to 30 minutes depending on the person.
        </p>
        <p>
          To begin, please press the button below.
        </p>
      </div>
      <button onclick="javascript:location.href='/condition1'">START</button>
    </div>

    <footer>
      &copy;2016 CHENLIZHAN ALL RIGHTS RESERVED
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>